ssName=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">\n                Drop a CSV here or click to browse\n              </span>\n              <input\n                type=\"file\"\n                accept=\".csv,text/csv\"\n                className=\"hidden\"\n                onChange={(e) => {\n                  const f = e.target.files?.[0];\n                  if (f) void onFile(f);\n                }}\n              />\n            </label>\n          </CardContent>\n        </Card>\n      )}\n\n      {step === 2 && (\n        <Card>\n          <CardHeader>\n            <CardTitle>Map columns</CardTitle>\n            <CardDescription>\n              Map each CSV column to a prospect or company field, or ignore it.\n            </CardDescription>\n          </CardHeader>\n          <CardContent className=\"space-y-4\">\n            <Table>\n              <TableHeader>\n                <TableRow>\n                  <TableHead>CSV column</TableHead>\n                  <TableHead>Maps to</TableHead>\n                </TableRow>\n              </TableHeader>\n              <TableBody>\n                {headers.map((col) => (\n                  <TableRow key={col}>\n                    <TableCell className=\"font-medium\">{col}</TableCell>\n                    <TableCell>\n                      <Select\n                        value={mapping[col] ?? \"ignore\"}\n                        onValueChange={(v) =>\n                          setMapping((m) => ({ ...m, [col]: v as ProspectCsvField }))\n                        }\n                      >\n                        <SelectTrigger>\n                          <SelectValue />\n                        </SelectTrigger>\n                        <SelectContent>\n                          {FIELD_OPTIONS.map((opt) => (\n                            <SelectItem key={opt.value} value={opt.value}>\n                              {opt.label}\n                            </SelectItem>\n                          ))}\n                        </SelectContent>\n                      </Select>\n                    </TableCell>\n                  </TableRow>\n                ))}\n              </TableBody>\n            </Table>\n            <div className=\"flex justify-end gap-2\">\n              <Button variant=\"outline\" onClick={() => setStep(1)}>\n                Back\n              </Button>\n              <Button onClick={() => void onMappingNext()}>Preview</Button>\n            </div>\n          </CardContent>\n        </Card>\n      )}\n\n      {step === 3 && parsed && (\n        <Card>\n          <CardHeader>\n            <CardTitle>Preview & validation</CardTitle>\n            <CardDescription>\n              {parsed.valid.length} valid · {parsed.invalid.length} invalid\n            </CardDescription>\n          </CardHeader>\n          <CardContent className=\"space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"flex gap-2\">\n              <Badge>{parsed.valid.length} valid</Badge>\n              <Badge variant={parsed.invalid.length ? \"destructive\" : \"secondary\"}>\n                {parsed.invalid.length} invalid\n              </Badge>\n            </div>\n            {parsed.invalid.length > 0 && (\n              <ul className=\"max-h-32 overflow-auto rounded border p-3 text-sm\">\n                {parsed.invalid.slice(0, 10).map((row) => (\n                  <li key={row.rowNumber}>\n                    Row {row.rowNumber}: {row.reason}\n                  </li>\n                ))}\n              </ul>\n            )}\n            <Table>\n              <TableHeader>\n                <TableRow>\n                  <TableHead>Email</TableHead>\n                  <TableHead>Name</TableHead>\n                  <TableHead>Company</TableHead>\n                </TableRow>\n              </TableHeader>\n              <TableBody>\n                {previewRows.map((row) => (\n                  <TableRow key={row.rowNumber}>\n                    <TableCell>{row.prospect.email}</TableCell>\n                    <TableCell>\n                      {[row.prospect.firstName, row.prospect.lastName].filter(Boolean).join(\" \")}\n                    </TableCell>\n                    <TableCell>{row.company?.name ?? row.company?.domain ?? \"—\"}</TableCell>\n                  </TableRow>\n                ))}\n              </TableBody>\n            </Table>\n            <div className=\"flex justify-end gap-2\">\n              <Button variant=\"outline\" onClick={() => setStep(2)}>\n                Back\n              </Button>\n              <Button onClick={() => setStep(4)}>Continue</Button>\n            </div>\n          </CardContent>\n        </Card>\n      )}\n\n      {step === 4 && (\n        <Card>\n          <CardHeader>\n            <CardTitle>Confirm import</CardTitle>\n            <CardDescription>\n              Importing {parsed?.valid.length ?? 0} rows from {file?.name}\n            </CardDescription>\n          </CardHeader>\n          <CardContent className=\"space-y-4\">\n            <div className=\"flex flex-col gap-2\">\n              <span className=\"text-sm font-medium\">Duplicate policy</span>\n              <Select\n                value={dedupePolicy}\n                onValueChange={(v) => setDedupePolicy(v as DedupePolicy)}\n              >\n                <SelectTrigger className=\"w-64\">\n                  <SelectValue />\n                </SelectTrigger>\n                <SelectContent>\n                  <SelectItem value=\"skip_existing\">Skip existing emails</SelectItem>\n                  <SelectItem value=\"update_existing\">Update existing emails</SelectItem>\n                </SelectContent>\n              </Select>\n            </div>\n            <div className=\"flex justify-end gap-2\">\n              <Button variant=\"outline\" onClick={() => setStep(3)}>\n                Back\n              </Button>\n              <Button disabled={importing} onClick={() => void onImport()}>\n                {importing ? \"Importing…\" : \"Run import\"}\n              </Button>\n            </div>\n          </CardContent>\n        </Card>\n      )}\n\n      {step === 5 && batchResult && (\n        <Card>\n          <CardHeader>\n            <CardTitle>Import complete</CardTitle>\n            <CardDescription>Batch {batchResult.id}</CardDescription>\n          </CardHeader>\n          <CardContent className=\"space-y-4\">\n            <dl className=\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-sm sm:grid-cols-4\">\n              <div>\n                <dt className=\"text-muted-foreground\">Created</dt>\n                <dd className=\"text-lg font-semibold\">{batchResult.createdCount}</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt className=\"text-muted-foreground\">Updated</dt>\n                <dd className=\"text-lg font-semibold\">{batchResult.updatedCount}</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt className=\"text-muted-foreground\">Skipped</dt>\n                <dd className=\"text-lg font-semibold\">{batchResult.skippedCount}</dd>\n              </div>\n              <div>\n                <dt className=\"text-muted-foreground\">Errors</dt>\n                <dd className=\"text-lg font-semibold\">{batchResult.erroredCount}</dd>\n              </div>\n            </dl>\n            {batchResult.errors.length > 0 && (\n              <Button variant=\"outline\" onClick={downloadErrors}>\n                <Download className=\"mr-2 h-4 w-4\" />\n                Download error CSV\n              </Button>\n            )}\n            <Button asChild>\n              <Link to=\"/prospects\">View prospects</Link>\n            </Button>\n          </CardContent>\n        </Card>\n      )}\n    </div>\n  );\n}\n","message":"The file /Users/beckett/.cursor/worktrees/quiksend/phase-2-prospects/apps/web/src/routes/_protected/prospects/import.tsx has been updated."}}},"hookAdditionalContexts":[],"toolCallId":"tool_39cf37ad-713a-45e9-8c45-c694dfb51ed","startedAtMs":"1782958034740","completedAtMs":"1782958038513"},"model_call_id":"5977d0c1-3ad5-42be-85f2-1e8828435224-45-j9qf","session_id":"6573c6ff-6012-4c40-8cb2-1911b390dd96","timestamp_ms":1782958038514}
